data.description: Check out this cute two-bedroom, one bath home with lots of recent updates including kitchen appliances, cabinets and countertops, bathroom vanity, some interior paint, carpet, and more.  The HVAC was replaced 5 years ago, and the roof is 4 years old. Plumbing was replaced 10 years ago, and the sewer lines were replaced 12 years ago. This home sits on a nice size lot with an attached carport, a nice patio perfect for a backyard cookout, a storage building, and it's fully fenced in front and back. Let's not forget the pecan tree! Call your favorite realtor to schedule a showing to see this great property.
